                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <b>Important :</b>
                            Join the Whatsapp community to receive the joining link, resources and webinar bonuses:
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
                            <a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/LhXgfArgkNBAFtxHQwkreu" class="p-2 rounded"
                               style="border: 1px solid green; background-color: #90EE90" target="_blank">Join the
